column3: Automatic sanity-testing: PASSED, see http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/4def248b2b47e5440b8ed53b9dd12e8303601eb0 for binaries and test log.\nThis test script verifies pulls every time they are updated. It, however, dies sometimes and fails to test properly.  If you are waiting on a test, please check timestamps to verify that the test.log is moving at http://jenkins.bluematt.me/pull-tester/cu
Closing in favor of #4160 which does the same but also removes unused stuff from bignum.h.\n
